{"analytics_identifier":"PB383","base_path":"/government/organisations/treasure-valuation-committee","content_id":"92cb30a3-5da7-4309-afcd-72603723ef3f","description":"The Treasure Valuation Committee (TVC), comprising of independent antiques or coin experts and a representative of the hobby of metal-detecting, establishes the likely market value of each treasure find. A reward of this value can then be made to the finders of treasure and to the owners of find sites unless there are grounds for no reward or a reduced award to be made. TVC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport .","details":{"acronym":"TVC","alternative_format_contact_email":"anna.payne@culture.gsi.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Treasure Valuation Committee (TVC), comprising of independent antiques or coin experts and a representative of the hobby of metal-detecting, establishes the likely market value of each treasure find. A reward of this value can then be made to the finders of treasure and to the owners of find sites unless there are grounds for no reward or a reduced award to be made.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Treasure Valuation Committee\">TVC</abbr> is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-culture-media-and-sport\">Department for Culture, Media and Sport</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-culture-media-sport","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Treasure Valuation Committee"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/treasure-valuation-committee/about/membership","title":"Membership"},{"href":"/government/organisations/treasure-valuation-committee/about/terms-of-reference","title":"Terms of reference"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_g